Class Downsampler

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.core.Downsampler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterator<DataPoint>, DataPoint, SeekableView
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FillingDownsampler

    public class Downsampler
extends Object
implements SeekableView, DataPoint
    Iterator that downsamples data points using an Aggregator.
